It goes further into
detail as you go into it,

00:12:35.487 --> 00:12:37.070
but again, that's
boring to show here.

00:12:37.070 --> 00:12:39.830
Nobody really wants to see that.

00:12:39.830 --> 00:12:42.510
But the best thing
is, it's a predictor.

00:12:42.510 --> 00:12:45.160
And this-- and in this
calculator, this spreadsheet--

