00:13:46.920 --> 00:13:48.170
What's the priority?

00:13:48.170 --> 00:13:50.000
It's all based on this.

00:13:50.000 --> 00:13:53.526
And the CFO knew that,
by increasing revenue,

00:13:53.526 --> 00:13:56.150
