helps with knowing

00:14:45.650 --> 00:14:48.860
who you should hire per a kind
of problem you have at the time

00:14:48.860 --> 00:14:50.360
and what levers
you want to pull.

00:14:50.360 --> 00:14:52.300
So for us, it was
partner channels,

00:14:52.300 --> 00:14:53.300
so that was really good.

